## Visualising data in scatterplot


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(data=exam_data, 
       aes(x= MATHS, 
           y=ENGLISH)) +
  geom_point()            
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](hands_on_ex1_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-12-1.png){width=672}
