## Combining boxplot with scatter plot


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(data=exam_data, 
       aes(y = MATHS, 
           x= GENDER)) +
  geom_boxplot() +                    
  geom_point(position="jitter", 
             size = 0.5)        
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](hands_on_ex1_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-13-1.png){width=672}
